Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.75,0:24:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这间旅馆里有一段回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.68,0:24:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的我 在跑着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.98,0:24:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 在跑着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没遇到小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.04,0:24:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会变成什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.57,0:24:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.48,0:24:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.67,0:24:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有些改变吧
